rows.label: qst002308_msg0001
rows.name:
Whoa! Who are you?! I-I
wasn't slacking off!

rows.label: qst002308_msg0002
rows.name:
Re-reporting? You're investigating
the warrior monks of Acedia?

rows.label: qst002308_msg0003
rows.name:
Okay... I'll tell you, so please don't
write about me in your article.

rows.label: qst002308_msg0004
rows.name:
There are twenty-three guards
at night. Is that enough?

rows.label: qst002308_msg0005
rows.name:
Anyway, I'm going back to my post,
so please, keep this a secret.
